! --- RT01 (エッジ・あなたの作業対象): アドレス/経路は構築済み(変更不可) ---
interface Loopback0
 ip address 1.1.1.1 255.255.255.255
!
interface {{ links[0] }}
 description === Uplink-A: to ISP-A (RT02) ===
 ip address 10.1.12.1 255.255.255.252
 no shutdown
!
interface {{ links[1] }}
 description === Uplink-B: to ISP-B (RT03) ===
 ip address 10.1.13.1 255.255.255.252
 no shutdown
!
router ospf 1
 router-id 1.1.1.1
 network 1.1.1.1 0.0.0.0 area 0
 network 10.1.12.0 0.0.0.3 area 0
 network 10.1.13.0 0.0.0.3 area 0
